  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "序一 探索东斯拉夫和基辅罗斯的历史奥秘",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300101063_3_425-469",
          "range": "425-469",
          "rangeStart": 425,
          "rangeEnd": 469,
          "markText": "斯拉夫人在历史上曾经与日耳曼人、凯尔特人被自恃“文明”的希腊人和罗马人视为三大“蛮族”。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1717645476,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-06 11:44:36",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=425&rangeEnd=469",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=425&rangeEnd=469"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_3_1430-1478",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1430-1478",
      "markText": "东斯拉夫人在6世纪时还没有国家，其社会制度大体处于由原始的氏族公社制社会向奴隶制社会过渡的时期。",
      "totalCount": 2140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1430&rangeEnd=1478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1430&rangeEnd=1478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_22_3651-3817",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3651-3817",
      "markText": "1067年，波洛茨克王公弗谢斯拉夫·布里亚奇斯拉维奇主动挑起内战，派兵占领了罗斯北部重镇诺夫哥罗德。",
      "totalCount": 2135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3651&rangeEnd=3817",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3651&rangeEnd=3817"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_20_3483-3523",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3483-3523",
      "markText": "罗斯大公国和拜占庭帝国在政治地位上应该是平等的，罗斯教会也不应该从属于希腊教会。",
      "totalCount": 2131,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3483&rangeEnd=3523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3483&rangeEnd=3523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_29_756-812",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "756-812",
      "markText": "穆斯季斯拉夫任命他的弟弟亚罗波尔克·弗拉基米罗维奇和尤里·弗拉基米罗维奇分别为佩列亚斯拉夫利王公和罗斯托夫王公。",
      "totalCount": 2117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=756&rangeEnd=812",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=756&rangeEnd=812"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_23_6824-6890",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "6824-6890",
      "markText": "伊兹雅斯拉夫一世战死之后，弗谢沃洛德·雅罗斯拉维奇是基辅王室中最年长者，顺理成章地继任基辅大公之位，历史上称其为“弗谢沃洛德一世”。",
      "totalCount": 2066,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6824&rangeEnd=6890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6824&rangeEnd=6890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_9_4457-4506",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4457-4506",
      "markText": "斯拉夫人不仅是勤劳倔强的农夫，更是经验丰富的猎人，驼鹿、梅花鹿、天鹅、鹅和野鸭都是他们的狩猎对象。",
      "totalCount": 2055,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4457&rangeEnd=4506",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4457&rangeEnd=4506"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_29_6100-6164",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "6100-6164",
      "markText": "如果说国家解体的苗头由于莫诺马赫和穆斯季斯拉夫等杰出领导者的存在而表现得还不是那么明显的话，那么当这些人去世后，解体则愈演愈烈。",
      "totalCount": 2022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=6100&rangeEnd=6164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=6100&rangeEnd=6164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_28_1366-1418",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1366-1418",
      "markText": "1113年4月16日，斯维亚托波尔克二世在维什戈罗德城突然去世，这让本身已经十分尖锐的社会矛盾更为严重。",
      "totalCount": 1982,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1366&rangeEnd=1418",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1366&rangeEnd=1418"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_9_4842-4871",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4842-4871",
      "markText": "部落中的公共耕地也越来越多地被分成以家庭为单位的独立地块。",
      "totalCount": 1975,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4842&rangeEnd=4871",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4842&rangeEnd=4871"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_6_10078-10112",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10078-10112",
      "markText": "公元前7—前5世纪，斯拉夫人已经掌握了从沼铁矿和湖矿中冶炼铁的方法。",
      "totalCount": 1957,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10078&rangeEnd=10112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10078&rangeEnd=10112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_19_7888-7926",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "7888-7926",
      "markText": "由于雅罗斯拉夫的王后英吉格尔达是瑞典国王的女儿，所以瑞典和罗斯一直关系密切。",
      "totalCount": 1935,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7888&rangeEnd=7926",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7888&rangeEnd=7926"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_21_7542-7614",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "7542-7614",
      "markText": "罗斯接受基督教后，许多古老的东斯拉夫城市开始衰落，旧的多神教圣地变得荒芜，原先居住在这里的多神教信徒纷纷去往其他地方去，一批新的城市发展起来了。",
      "totalCount": 1909,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7542&rangeEnd=7614",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7542&rangeEnd=7614"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_21_5495-5558",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "5495-5558",
      "markText": "院中一般都有一座高大的木制塔楼建筑，该独立建筑由许多房间组成，有带壁炉可供取暖的房间，也有不带壁炉的房间，以及冷藏室和储藏室。",
      "totalCount": 1902,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_9_2698-2739",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2698-2739",
      "markText": "波利安人、谢维利安人、拉迪米奇人、维亚迪奇人长期以来一直向哈扎尔人进贡松鼠和貂皮；",
      "totalCount": 1884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2698&rangeEnd=2739",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2698&rangeEnd=2739"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_32_3882-3948",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "3882-3948",
      "markText": "截至2020年，在诺夫哥罗德已经发现了1100多份桦树皮文献，在俄罗斯、乌克兰和白俄罗斯的其他城市也相继发现了100多份这样的文书。",
      "totalCount": 1859,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=3882&rangeEnd=3948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=3882&rangeEnd=3948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_9_7834-7886",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "7834-7886",
      "markText": "随着手工业品需求的大量增加，手工业者逐步从农业劳动中脱离出来，工匠已经可以通过手工业劳动养活自己和家人。",
      "totalCount": 1848,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7834&rangeEnd=7886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7834&rangeEnd=7886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_7_5092-5149",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5092-5149",
      "markText": "犹太人作为商人、工匠和高利贷者在南俄地区非常活跃，在博斯普鲁斯王国和希腊的其他城市中都能找到犹太人的祈祷室和会堂。",
      "totalCount": 1840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5092&rangeEnd=5149",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5092&rangeEnd=5149"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_7_417-489",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "417-489",
      "markText": "日复一日，年复一年，游牧部落突破乌拉尔山脉南部和里海之间宽阔自由的通道，从亚洲内陆进入东欧平原，而东斯拉夫人的祖先则是阻止他们前进的第一道屏障。",
      "totalCount": 1837,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=417&rangeEnd=489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=417&rangeEnd=489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_32_2277-2413",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "2277-2413",
      "markText": "从“红太阳”弗拉基米尔一世时期开始，大批拜占庭、保加利亚和塞尔维亚的宗教学者、翻译家来到罗斯，在“智者”雅罗斯拉夫、弗谢沃洛德一世、莫诺马赫和穆斯季斯拉夫一世统治时代，大批希腊文和保加利亚文的宗教文献和世俗书籍被翻译过来，其中也包括许多拜占庭的历史著作和基督教圣徒的传记。",
      "totalCount": 1822,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2277&rangeEnd=2413",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2277&rangeEnd=2413"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101063_9_10206-10246",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10206-10246",
      "markText": "总的来说，东斯拉夫人的社会发展水平落后于法兰克、英格兰、拜占庭帝国和阿拉伯帝国。",
      "totalCount": 1819,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101063&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10206&rangeEnd=10246",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b2032190813ab8dfag013324?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10206&rangeEnd=10246"
    }
  ],
